details.message:
`001.008.004 Mk_Workstages_Attrib`
- Test assigns 8 attributes of data types: string, date, datetime, integer, float, boolean, money, and image.
- "Stage A", "Stage B", and "Stage C" all have these 8 attributes.
- Each attribute follows the naming convention of SMCT_DATATYPE.
- To create attributes, see `003.001.002`.
